data.description: Flexible Living: A two-story townhome with a finished basement, adaptable for a 4th bedroom or family room, including a bathroom. This layout caters to diverse lifestyles. Easy Maintenance: Snow removal, lawn care, and exterior upkeep are taken care of, providing a carefree lifestyle, allowing you more time for what matters. Community Oasis: Enjoy a swimming pool, clubhouse, and pickleball court, fostering community bonds and recreational opportunities. Convenient Locale: Proximity to shopping, entertainment, and freeways adds practicality, saving time and effort in your daily routines. Laundry Efficiency: Second-floor laundry near bedrooms streamlines chores, eliminating the need for stairs. Modern Kitchen: An open floor plan integrates a stylish eat-in kitchen with a pantry, modern appliances, and quartz countertops. Luxurious Main Suite: The spacious main bedroom and ensuite, featuring a tile shower and floors, provide a touch of luxury and a private retreat. Pet-Friendly Vibes: Pets are genuinely welcomed, creating a warm and inclusive environment for furry family members. Below Market Value: Priced attractively below market value, this townhome offers a premium living experience without straining your budget. In essence, this townhome blends versatility, convenience, and luxury, from its flexible layout to community amenities, modern kitchen, and pet-friendly policy, all at a compelling price point below market value.
